      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation via benchmark test cases documented in vendor verification manual.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verification manual benchmark results reviewed and confirmed for rotating machinery and viscous flow cases. Required level 1 achieved."
