      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index for hemolysis index QoI must be below 5% on the production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed. GCI on fine mesh (21.6M cells) is 2.1% for hemolysis index, meeting the 5% threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirms monotonic convergence."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
