      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match simulated operating envelope within documented tolerances for flow rate and rotational speed.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments conducted at 2.5, 4.0, and 6.0 L/min at 2500 and 3500 RPM. Simulation boundary conditions set to match these nominal values. Flow measurement uncertainty ±2% documented. All test conditions treated as correctly applied; no operator misapplication scenarios modeled."
    },
    {
