      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted RH index must agree with experimental RH index within 15% across all validation operating points.",
      "rationale": "Simulated RH index compared against FDA benchmark at three flow rates. Maximum deviation 9.3%. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all points. Agreement within the 15% acceptance band at MRL 2."
    },
    {
