      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI (relative hemolysis index) must be directly linked to the clinical decision criterion and traceable to the COU acceptance criterion RH < 1.",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index is the primary regulatory metric for CPB device clearance. QoI is directly mapped to the COU acceptance criterion. Traceability documented in model report."
