      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must use the same pump geometry family and overlapping operating conditions as the COU.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used in both validation experiments and COU simulations. Operating envelope overlap confirmed for flow and speed ranges. Validation relevance to COU demonstrated."
