      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key model inputs (blood viscosity, density, pump geometry dimensions) must be traceable to measured or literature-sourced values with documented uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Blood density 1056 kg/m3 and Carreau-Yasuda viscosity parameters sourced from peer-reviewed literature. Pump geometry from FDA-released CAD files. Input uncertainty documented via sensitivity analysis showing hemolysis index variation < 6% across input ranges."
    },
