    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven credibility factors assessed and meeting required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. Discretization error, output comparison, and model form factors all demonstrate adequate credibility for the CPB hemolysis COU. Use-error evaluation is noted as covered by IEC 62366 in a companion document; no formal link is provided but the team accepted this reference as sufficient for the current submission. Overall credibility package judged adequate to support the Class II device tolerance decision at the stated model risk level.",
